name: CGImageMetadataErrors
desc: Constants for errors that occur when getting or setting metadata information.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: An error that indicates an unknown condition occurred.

items.name: case unsupportedFormat
items.desc: An error that indicates the metadata was in an unsupported format.

items.name: case badArgument
items.desc: An error that indicates a parameter was malformed or contained invalid data.

items.name: case conflictingArguments
items.desc: An error that indicates an attempt to save conflicting metadata values.
